<p>
The Task Management To-Do System is a collaborative web application that will provide a one-stop shop for managing your To Do Lists for your project. This application will allow users to:<ul>
<li>Create projects</li><li>Assign users to a project</li><li>Assign tasks and subtasks</li><li>Assign timelines to a project</li><li>Add notes</li><li>Assign a status</li><li>View reports</li>
</ul></p>

Projects will also be able to be updated with pertinent details by the Project Manager or by a person assigned to a task in the project. And, finally, administrators will have the ability to delete projects or tasks, as needed.



